page.title: 09HOME LIFE
page.content: When i get home,i like to play with our pets.We have a dog and a cat.We play games on our computer too,and we also watch films on the television.I go to Pilots club on Thursday evenings ,and my hobby is riding moter bikes, but i dont have a B.M.X bike.I go out riding a lot.I have moter bike pictures on my walls,and i have lots of magazines,I play outside most nights,and we go fishing a lot down the river or for walks through the fields.Lots of the other children are in the Cubs,Brownies,Girls Brigade, Badminton Club or Dance classes,and these are all in the evenings after school.
